 the name of taxes or management fees.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Translate by Humans translators are also knowledgeable about SEO requirements and if the text is for a website/software/app, they ensure it is optimized for good search results.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/tbh.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1393606\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/tbh-300x191.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"191\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/tbh-300x191.png 300w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/tbh-150x95.png 150w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/tbh.png 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you are already a WPML user and interested in using Translate by Humans for translation, follow the instructions for</span><a href=\"https://wpml.org/translation-service/translate-by-humans/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> translating WordPress sites with Translate by Humans</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and <strong>get a free translation sample of 150 &#8211; 200 words</strong> to check quality and service. If you are new to WPML, feel free to purchase the</span><a href=\"https://wpml.org/purchase/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Multilingual CMS</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> package and get started.</span></p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=v05Mqny67AQ:fJI4YV5EqFw:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=v05Mqny67AQ:fJI4YV5EqFw:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=v05Mqny67AQ:fJI4YV5EqFw:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=v05Mqny67AQ:fJI4YV5EqFw:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" bor